https://leetcode.com/problems/reverse-integer/

My Solution:

Thought：
	注意题目要求：翻转后的数如果integer overflow，返回0。
		
Code：
class Solution {
public:
	int reverse(int x)
	{
		long long ans = 0;
		
		while (x)
		{
			ans = ans * 10 + x % 10;
            if(ans > 2147483647 || ans < -2147483648)
                return 0;
			x /= 10;
		}
		return ans;
	}
};

Performance:
	Runtime:12ms, beats 98.25%
	Memory:13.9MB, beats 65.18%
		
Superior Solution:
	无